General Motors Co. (GM)  is evaluating a
potential closure of two of Adam Opel GmbHâ€™s plants in  Europe  at
a cost of 1.5 billion euros ($2 billion),  Handelsblatt  reported.  The factories in Ellesmere Port in the U.K and Bochum in
